  "description": "Create a visual diagram (Mermaid format in docs/) showing the flow of state between Rust AppState, Tauri events, Zustand slices, and React components. Highlights which state is synchronous via invoke() vs async via events.\n\n**Rationale:** The dual-language, dual-store architecture is complex. A diagram helps developers mentally model how recording state propagates from cpal through whisper to the UI without tracing through multiple files.",
